config BR2_PACKAGE_ROCKNIX_JOYPAD
    bool "rocknix-joypad"
    depends on BR2_LINUX_KERNEL
    help
      Linux kernel driver for various handheld devices.
      Provides input support for analog sticks connected via
      ADC and Multiplexers, and buttons via GPIO.
      Thanks Rocknix team!
      
      https://github.com/ROCKNIX/rocknix-joypad

comment "rocknix-joypad needs a Linux kernel to be built"
	depends on !BR2_LINUX_KERNEL
